messages.message: Thanks for trying and sharing the feedback, @jack.robbins! Integration with Jira is part of the Search roadmap.

@Balaram In research mode, the same OCR query returned more tickets (15), and most (10) were relevant to OCR. It's an improvement, but still some ways to go, as the first returned ticket in the list was about _Support for XSLM file extension_
Thanks for your feedback! I will work with the team on the next steps
